values:
i went biking today.
my leg hair is long again.
i can feel it actually flowing in the wind.
-------------------------------------------------
the boy took the bike and i say he's no better than the original theif.

at work, there are is a large amount of carelessness to observe. the lady of "m" wlks with a sway and never thinks to listen to his words.
she talks and listens while her eyes move about.
she is not really listening.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------.
there is a man screaming outside my window.
he is yelling at his girlfriend for money.
i hope she slaps him in the face.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------.
he has laugh lines that make me snicker in delight.
especially when they are an inch away from my childish lines.
